description: Not only is Crepe and Cake the only French Food Truck in the Twin Cities, but it happens to be home to the most delicious crepes you may ever taste. Locals absolutely adore their authentic selection of sweet and savory perfection, with toppings ranging from pistachio butter or Nutella, to pesto & gruyere. All are able to enjoy these wonderful treats, as you’re welcome to opt for Gluten Free.  This truck can be found at several farmers' markets throughout Minnesota, and they’re available for private events, so they’ll happily bring this fantastic French food straight over to you. When it comes to having mastered “The Fine Art of French Crepes”, this truck undoubtedly takes the cake.
name: Crepe and Cake
